cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DM, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a new learning approach for feature selection using particle swarm optimization. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of swarm intelligence and optimization techniques also suggests the sub-category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper also evaluates the proposed approach using benchmark datasets, indicating the sub-category of data mining (cs.DM). Finally, the use of feature selection in classification tasks suggests the sub-category of computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
